  15 May 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> files/lvm2.rc6:
  Start before checkfs.

  14 May 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> lvm2-1.95.10.ebuild,
  files/lvm2.rc6:
  Add startup script.

